TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlStatement select distinct LP.LAST_MODIFIED as lastModifiedDateTime, LP."NAME" as ServiceName, dbms_lob.getlength(LP."DATA") as ServiceSize, LUX.USER_NAME as LastModifiedUser from LSW_PROCESS LP, LSW_USR_XREF LUX where LUX.USER_ID = LP.LAST_MODIFIED_BY_USER_ID and dbms_lob.getlength(LP."DATA") > ? order by dbms_lob.getlength(LP."DATA") desc
